Package net.adoptopenjdk.v3.api

Class AOV3Release.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.adoptopenjdk.v3.api.AOV3Release.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    AOV3Release
    public static final class AOV3Release.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds instances of type AOV3Release. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.

        public final AOV3Release.Builder from​(AOV3ReleaseType instance)
